"between the domains. The following command demonstrates an open channel "
"between dom0 and someVM (in this case, a remote shell):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/services/qrexec.rst:35 31ccb3e82c1f4581b42b416953b3a875
msgid ""
"The ``qvm-run`` command is heavily based on ``qrexec-client``. It also "
"handles additional activities, e.g. starting the domain if the domain is not"
" up yet and starting the GUI daemon. It is usually more convenient to use "
"``qvm-run``."
